name: Tezpunks
description:
Tezpunks

Year AD 7702, a group of deadly punks with superpowers are assigned a mysterious mission.  
Objectives of the mission will be communicated to them from the command center.For now,the only objective communicated to the punks is to time travel to 2021. 

ID #013
Male

Name         : Alsyb 
Strength     : 95/100
Intelligence : 79/100

Alsyb was the king of Olnoyenne. His brothers killed him and buried his body behind the temple of goddess Xaica, the goddess of love. They also buried alive everyone who was closely associated with the king, including his 7 year old son and his pet crocodile.The burial was found by the Guharv twins and all the dead souls were brought back from the underworld and reunited with their bodies.
